quran[128]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Yamiroore Alla nde ari wota on hawjan nde. senaaree woodanii mo! o toowii e ko …ďe cirkata.ko."
  16,2,"Homo jippinira maleykaaji …ói e wayhu on e yamiroore makko, dow mo muuyi e jeyaa…ďe makko …ďeen, won¬īde : ""Jertinree wiide dewetee…óo alaa si wonaa min. Kulee kam""."
  16,3,"O tagiri kammuuli …óiin e leydi ndin goonga. o toowii e ko …ďe sirkoobe cirkata ko."
  16,4,"O tagiri ne…ó…óaŇčke iwde e to…ď…ďere (maniiyu); jaka yoo kaŇčko ko wennjoowo …ďanngu…óo.pee√Ī…óo"
  16,5,"Neemoraa…ói …óin, o tagani on …ói; no e majji nguli nugguki e nafooje. Ko e majji kadi √Īaamoton."
  16,6,"Hino woodani on e majji cu…óaari, tuma njofnoton …ói e tuma oornoton …ói."
  16,7,"Hi…ói ndoono doŇčle mon na…ďa e leydi ndi on njotto- tanooko si wanaa e tampere pittaali. Pellet, Joomi mon ko O Yurmetee…óo Hinnotoo…óo."
  16,8,"E pucci, e mbam-pucci, e mbabbi, fii yo on mba…ó…óo …ói, e cu…óaari. Himo taga kadi ko on nganndaa."
  16,9,"Ko Alla woodani …ďanngingol laawol poocciingol ngol, no e majji ngol feewaani. Si o muuyuno, o fewnat on denndaangal."
  16,10,"Ko KaŇčko woni jippinir…óo ndiyam ka kammu, hino woodani on e majjam njaram, le…ó…óe no (yalta) e majjam, ko e majjam kadi oornoton."
  16,11,"Homo fu…ónirana on …óam aawruuji, nebbanteeje, e tamarooje, e inabuuje, e kala dim…óe.…ďesnoje wonii e …óuum, tasakuyee wonan¬īde yim…ďe miijitotoo…ďe."
  16,12,"O eltani on jemma on e √Īalawma on; naange ngen e lewru nduun. Koode …óeen kadi ko eltiraa…óe yamiroore makko. Wonii e …óuum, tasakuyeeji wonan¬īde yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe."
  16,13,"E ko o tagani on kon ka leydi ceertu…óum nooneeji. wonii e …óuum, tasakuyee wonan¬īde yim…ďe waajitorat…ďe."
  16,14,"Ko KaŇčko woni eltan…óo on maayo ngon fii yo on √Īaam e maggo teewu keccu, yaltinon e maggo cu…óaari ndi …ďornoto…óon. A yi'ay laa…óe no fe∆ī∆īa e maggo, e fii yo on …óa…ď…ďu e …ďural makko ngal, belejo'o, on njettat [mo]."
  16,15,"O tuti penle ka leydi fii wata …óe dillidu e mo'on, e caatli, e …óate, belejo'o on peeway."
  16,16,"e maandeeji [laawi]. Koode …óen he…ďe …óowora …óe."
  16,17,"E hara tagoowo on wa'ay wa on tagataa? E on mbaactotaako?"
  16,18,"Si on limtii doke Alla …óe, on moftataa …ói. Pellet, Alla ko jaafotoo…óo, jurmotoo…óo."
  16,19,"Alla no anndi ko cuu…óoton e ko pe√Ī√Īinton."
  16,20,"∆äiin …ói …ďe ndewata ga ni Alla, …ói tagataa hay huunde, kaŇčji tigi ko …ói tagetee…ói."
  16,21,"Ko…ói maay…ói …ói nguuraani, …ďe so'aa-anndude (…ďetinaani)de …ďe mmintintee."
  16,22,"dewetee…óo mon on ko dewetee…óo gooto. …ďeen …ďe ngooŇč…óinaa laakara, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ko jeddu…óe, …ďen ko townitii…ďe."
  16,23,"Sikke alaa won¬īde Alla no anndi ko …ďe cuu…óata e ko …ďe pe√Ī√Īinta. KaŇčko O yi…óaa townitii…ďe …ďen."
  16,24,"Si …ďe mbianaama : ""Ko hol…óum Joomi mon jippini?"" ∆Āe mbi'a: ""Ko tinndi adinoo…ďe!""."
  16,25,"Fii yo …ďe ndoondo bakkaatuuji ma…ď…ďe …óiin fof √Īande Darngal, e bakkaatuuji …ďeen …ďe majjinirta ko aldaa e ganndal; nganndee bonii ko …ďe ndonndoytoo."
  16,26,"GooŇč…óii …ďeen adinoo…ďe …ďe pewjiino, Alla jirbiniri mahdeele ma…ď…ďe …óeen ka doose. Kippoodi ndin yanti e ma…ď…ďe, lepte …óen ardirani …ďe nokku ka …ďe so'aa-aanndude(.tinaani.)"
  16,27,"Refti √Īande darngal, O hoynoyay…ďe, O wi'ana…ďe: Ko holto kafidaa…ói am …óiin …ói ha…ďirayno…óon fii mum?"" …ďeen okkaa…ďe ganndal mbi'a: ""Koyeera on hannde e bone on wonii e heefer…ďe …ďen""."
  16,28,"∆Āeen …ďen maleykaaji …ďen hunnata, too√Īu…ďe ko'e-mun, …ďe werloo jebbilraare, (…ďe mbia): ""min ngoonaa- no gollatnoo…ďe ko boni!"" -""wonaa non woniri, pellet Alla ko ngandu…óo ko huuwayno…óon"".(ngollatn…óon.)"
  16,29,"Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen luttugol ton. Nge bonii √Īaa∆īorde wonan¬īde townitii…ďe …ďen."
  16,30,"Wi'anee …ďeen gooŇč…óu…ďe: ""Ko hol…óuum Joomi mon jippini?"" ∆Āe mbi'a: ""Ko mo∆ī∆īere"". Hono woodani …ďen mo∆ī∆īin…ďe aduna …óoo mo∆ī∆īere; pellet ko saare laakara nden …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude. nde mo∆ī∆īii saare gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen."
  16,31,"Aljannaaji duumal, he…ďe naati …ói, caatli no ila ley majji. Hino woodani …ďe toon kala ko …ďe paaletee; ko wano nii Alla yo…ďirta gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen."
  16,32,"∆Āeen …ďe maleykaaji …ói mbarata hara ko …ďe laa…ď…ďe- …ďe mbi'an […ďen]: ""Kisiyee wonii e mon! Naatiree Aljanna on, sabu ko ngollatno…óon kon"".e"
  16,33,"Hara […ďee sirkoo…ďe fenna] hino habbitii si wonaa nde maleykaaji …ói ngarata e ma…ď…ďe, maa yami- roore Joomi maa ndeen ara? Ko wano noon …ďen adinoo…ďe …ďe wa…óirnoo. Alla too√Īaani …ďe; si ko woni, ko ko'e ma…ď…ďe …ďe wonnoo e too√Īu…ďe."
  16,34,"Boneeji …ói …ďe huuwi …óin memi …ďen, kon ko …ďe njalkitatnoo jippii e ma…ď…ďe."
  16,35,"∆Āeen sirku…ďe mbi'i: ""Sinno Alla muuyuno, men ndewataano ga ni makko hay huunde, wonaa minen wanaa baabiraa…ďe amen; min karmintaa- no gaanin makko hay huunde"". Ko wano non adi- noo…ďe …ďeen gerdunoo. taw si no fawiiii nulaa…ďe …ďen si wonaa jottingol …ďanngina?"
  16,36,"GooŇč…óii min imminii e kala mofte nulaa…óo, won¬īde ndewee Alla, ngo…ó…óito…óon bewnay…ói …óin. Hino e ma…ď…ďe on Mo Alla feewni, hino e ma…ď…ďe kadi on mo majjere ndeen jojji e mum. Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron ko honno battane yeddunoo…ďe …ďeen wa'unoo."
  16,37,"Si a reer…óii e peewal ma…ď…ďe, [anndu] pellet, Alla feewnataa on mo o majjini, alanaa …ďe kadi walloo…ďe."
  16,38,"∆Āe ngoo…óndirii Alla ha…ótirde goo…óndooje ma…ď…ďe: ""Alla immintintaa on maayu…óo"". Wanaa non! ∆äuum ko fodoore goonga ka makko, ko woni tan, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďe nganndaa."
  16,39,"(O immintiniroyay …ďe) fii yo O …ďannginan …ďe ko …ďe luutondiratnoo e mum. e fii yo …ďeen yeddu…ďe anndu won¬īde hari ko …ďe jeddunoo…ďe."
  16,40,"nganndee daalol amen wonan¬īde huunde, si min faandike nde, min mbianat nde tan: ""Laato"", nde laatoo."
  16,41,"∆Āeen fernoo…ďe fii Alla, …ďaawo …ďe too√Īaama, ma min ho…ónu …ďe ka aduna (e weerde) mo∆ī∆īere. Pellet, ko njo…ďdi laakara ndin …ďuri mawnude, si tawno he…ďe nganndi."
  16,42,"∆Āeen mu√Ī√Īii…ďe, e tuugii e Joomi ma…ď…ďe."
  16,43,"Min nulaani ado maa…óa si wanaa wor…ďe, min wahayina e ma…ď…ďe. Lanndee yim…ďe defte …ďeen si wonii on nganndaa."
  16,44,"(Men nulirii …ďe) …ďanngudi e defte. min njippini e maa…óa janngeteende nden, fii yo a …ďannginan yim…ďe …ďeen kon ko jippinaa e ma…ď…ďe, belejo'o kam…ďe …ďe miijitoto."
  16,45,"E hara …ďeen fewju…ďe boneeji …óiin kooli won¬īde Alla munnirtaa …ďe leydi ndin, maa lepte …óeen ngardirana …ďe nokku mo …ďe so'aa-anndude,(…ďetinaani)."
  16,46,"maa o nanngira …ďe yahdu ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ngonaani laawotoo…ďe."
  16,47,"Maa O nanngira …ďe e hoore kulol. anndu Joomi mon ko Yurmetee…óo, jurmotoo…óo."
  16,48,"E …ďee njii'aani ko Alla tagi kon e huunde nde …óow…óe mun yiiltondirta √Īaamo e nano, sujjangol Alla, hara ko …ói jankinii…ói."
  16,49,"Ko Alla woni ko sujjanta kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, immorde e ruugayngel, e maleykaaji …ďen, kam…ďe …ďe townitotaako.(mawnakintaako.)"
  16,50,"He…ďe kulira Joomi ma…ď…ďe, senngo dow ma…ď…ďe, he…ďe mba…óa ko …ďe njamiraa."
  16,51,"Alla daali: ""Wota on njogito rewetee…ďe …ói…óo. ngnndee KaŇčko ko O deewetee…óo gooto. Ko min ngoni ko kuloton""."
  16,52,"Ko KaŇčko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi; ko KaŇčko …óoftagol duumiingol tabitani. E ko ko woori Alla kuloton?"
  16,53,"Kala ko ke…ď…óon e neema ko immorde ka Alla. refti si lorra memii on, ko Ka makko ngullitoto…óon."
  16,54,"Refti si o huncanii on lorra kan, e jaka fedde goo e mo'on, ko sirkanoo…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe."
  16,55,"Fii yo …ďe njeddu ko min ngokki …ďe kon. Awa ndakmitee, arma nganndon."
  16,56,"He…ďe mba…óana huunde nde …ďe nganndaa ge…óal e kon ko min arsiki …ďe. Wallaahi! On lannditete e kon ko pekindotono…óon."
  16,57,"He…ďe mba…óana Alla …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe. senaare woodanii mo He…ďe (wa…óana) ko'e ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe woo…óitii."
  16,58,"Si gooto e ma…ď…ďe weltiniraama …ďi…ó…óo debbo, yeeso makko ngon wa…ótina wayliingo …ďalewo e, hara ko o suu…ó-suno."
  16,59,"Homo suu…óora yim…ďe …ďeen, sabu bone mo o weltiniraa oon. E o jogitoray mo e hoore koyeera kaa o uway mo ka leydi? ngannde bonii ko …ďe √Īaawata!"
  16,60,"Hino woodani …ďeen …ďe ngooŇč…óinaa laakara sifa bon…óo on. Ko Alla woodani sifa toow…óo on. Ko KaŇčko kadi woni pool…óo, √Īee√Ī…óo."
  16,61,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yim…ďe …ďeen sabu too√Īe ma…ď…ďe …óen, O ccataano e dow mayri ruugayngel. Ko woni tun, Himo nee…ďtinana …ďe haa e lajal gannda- ngal. Si lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal arii, …ďe nee…ďnantaake yonta …ďe adintinantaake."
  16,62,"Hi…ďe mba…óana Alla ko …ďe nga√Īanta [ko'e-ma…ď…ďe]. ∆äem…óe ma…ď…ďe no cifoo fenaande, won¬īde no woodani …ďe mo∆ī∆īere. Sikke alaa won¬īde no woodani …ďe Yiite, e won¬īde ko …ďe …óalii…ďe."
  16,63,"Wallaahi! GooŇč…óii min nulii e mofte adinoo…ďe ma, seytaane cu…óani …ďe ngolle ma…ď…ďe …óen. Ko kaŇčko woni gi…óo ma…ď…ďe hannde, hino woodani …ďe lepte muus…óe."
  16,64,"Min jippiniraali deftere nden e maa…óa si wonaa fii yo a …ďannginan …ďe kon ko …ďe luutondiri e mun, kadi ko nde peewal, e yurmeende wonan¬īde yim…ďe goo…óin…ďe …ďeen."
  16,65,"Alla jippinirii ka kammu ndiyam, O wuurnitiri …óam leydi ndin …ďaawo ndi yoorde. wonii e …óuum, maande wonan¬īde yim…ďe nanoo…ďe."
  16,66,"Hino woodani on e neemoraa…ói …óiin tasakuyee: mi…óen njarna on e ko woni e deedi majji, - hakkunde coowo e ∆īii∆īam - …ďiraa…óam laa…ďu…óam, wel…óam fii yaroo…ďe."
  16,67,"E dim…óe tamarooji e inabuuje, ho…óon jogitora …óam siwran e arsike mo∆ī∆īo. wonii e …óuum, maande wonan¬īde yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe."
  16,68,"Joomi maa wahayini e √Īaakii ngii, won¬īde : ""Jaggu ka pelle cuu…ói, e le…ó…óe …óen, e kon ko …ďe ca√Īata."
  16,69,"Refti √Īaamaa e kala dim…óe …óen, naaton e …óate Joomi mon newinaa…óe. Hino yalta e deedi majji [kannji √Īaaki …óin], njaram seru…óam nooneeji mun, no e majjam cellal wonan¬īde yim…ďe …ďen. Wonii e …óuum, maande wonan¬īde yim…ďe miijitotoo…ďe."
  16,70,"Alla tagii on, refti O hunnay on. Hino e moo…óon on ruttetee…óo e jaasu…óum nguurndam, fii wata o anndu huunde …ďaawo ganndal [makko aranal]. Pellet, Alla ko ganndu…óo, kattan…óo."
  16,71,"Alla …ďurnii yoga mon e dow yoga ka arsike. ∆Āurnaa…ďe …ďen ngonaani ruttiroo…ďe arsike ma…ď…ďe on e …ďeen …ďe jeytiri √Īaame ma…ď…ďe …óen haa …ďe pota e mayri. E ko dokke Alla on …ďe njeddata?"
  16,72,"Alla wa…óiranii on e woŇčkiiji mon …óiin resondir…ďe, o wa…óirani on e resondiraa…ďe mon …ďen …ďi…ó…ďe e taaniraa…ďe, o arsiki on immorde e laa…ďu…ói. E ko meere nden …ďe gooŇč…óinta? E ko neema Alla on kam…ďe …ďe njeddata?"
  16,73,"He…ďe ndewa gaanin makko, huunde nde waawanaa …ďe (addude) arsike ka kammuuli e ka leydi hay huunde, …ói kattanaaka […óum]."
  16,74,"Wata on mba…óan Alla yerodniraa…ói. Pellet, Alla ko ganndu…óo, onon on nganndaa."
  16,75,"Alla piyii misal maccu…óo jeyaa…óo, mo waawaa hay huunde, e on mo min arsiki immorde e amen arsike mo∆ī∆īo, hara on wintoo e …óuum gunndoo e kene. Hara …ďeen no fota? Yettooree woodanii Alla! Ko woni, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe anndaa."
  16,76,"Alla piyi kadi misal wor…ďe …ói…óo: go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe ko mbobo, o waawaa hay huunde, kaŇčko ko o donngal e hoore jey…óo mo on; nokku kala ka on fewtiniri mo, o addataa mo∆ī∆īere; hara on …óon fotay e on yamiroowo nuun…óal, hara himo e laawol pocciingol?"
  16,77,"Ko Alla woodani wirnii…ói kammmuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Fiyaaku Darngal ngal wonaani si wonaa yeru kin∆īan yiitere maa hara ko ka√Īun …ďuri …ďa…ótaade. Pellet, Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde."
  16,78,"Alla yaltinii on ka deedi neeniraa…ďe mon, on anndaa huunde, O wa…óani on nan…óe, e gii…óe e …ďer…óe, belejo'o, on yettay [Mo]."
  16,79,"E …ďe nji'aani colli …óiin ko …ói eltaa…ói ka weeyo kammu (won¬īde) jogitaaki …ói si wanaa Alla? Wonii e …óuum, maandeeji wonan¬īde yim…ďe gooŇč…óinoo…ďe …ďen."
  16,80,"Alla wa…óanii on e cuu…ói mon …óin ko…óorle, O wa…óani on e guri neemoraa…ói …óin tillisaaji …ói taggoton √Īande eggoton e √Īande ko…ótoton. No e lee…ďi (baali) …óin, e lee…ďi (geloo…ói) …óin e lee…ďi (dammi) …óiin nda…ó…óudi [suudu] e dakmitor…ói haa e saanga."
  16,81,"Alla wa…óanii on e ko o tagi kon …óow…óe. O wa…óani on e pelle …óeen cuu…óor…óe. O wa…óani on comci da…ónday…ói on nguleendi, e conci da…ónday…ói on e hare mon. Ko wano nii o timminirta dokke makko …óeen e dow mon, mbelejo'o on njebbiloto."
  16,82,"Si …ďe nduŇčtiima, anndu ko fawi maa, ko yottingol …ďanngina (pee√Īngol.)"
  16,83,"He…ďe nganndi dokke Alla …óeen; refti …ďe njedda …óe. Ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe ko heefer…ďe."
  16,84,"(JaŇčto) kadi √Īande min immintinoyta e kala mofte seedeejo, refti …ďeen yeddu…ďe sakkitoyantaake (ngantinagol), wanaa kam…ďe ngoni ko …óa…ď…ďiroytee ruttitagol [e yarluyee Joomi ma…ď…ďe]."
  16,85,"Si too√Īu…ďe …ďeen ynj'ii lepte …óeen, …ďe hoynantaake, lepte wanaa …ďe nee…ďnitantee…ďe."
  16,86,"Si sirkoo…ďe …ďeen nji*i kafidaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen, …ďe mbi'a: ""Joomi amen, ko …óii woni kafidaa…ói amen …ói men ndrewaynoo gah ni ma"". [Kafidaa…ói ma…ď…ďe] …óiin njilta e ma…ď…ďe konngol ngol: ""Onon ko on fenoo…ďe""."
  16,87,"∆Āe mbernoo e Alla ndeen √Īalnde jebbilaare, kon ko pekindotonoo majjira …ďe."
  16,88,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe …ďe paddii e laawol Alla ngol, min …ďeydiranii …ďe lepte e hoore lepte, sabu ko …ďe bonniraynoo kon."
  16,89,"(JaŇčto kadi) √Īande minn immintinoyta e kala mofte ko seeditoo e ma…ď…ďe, jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, min ngadda maa [an Muhammadu] ko seeditoo e …ďee …óoo. min njippini e maa…óa deftere nden, ko nde …ďannginoore kala huunde, e peewal, e yurmeende, e welo-welo wonan¬īde juul…ďe …ďen."
  16,90,"Tabitii Alla yamirii nuun…óal, e mo∆ī∆īingol, e mo∆ī∆īagol e joomiraa…ďe …ďadondiral. homo ha…óa gaay e pan-kare, e ko a√Īinii, e bewre. homo waajoo on, mbeleejo'o, on mbaajitoray."
  16,91,"kuu…ďnee ahadi Alla ndiin si on ahodaama, wata on pirtu goo…óndooje …óeen …ďaawo …óe tenntineede, gooŇč…óii on mba…óii Alla seedanii…óo [on e hunnugol ngol]. Pellet, ko ganndu…óo ko ngolloton."
  16,92,"Wota on ngon wano (debbo) pirtunoo…óo mottawol mun …ďaawo doole firtude, ho…óon njogitora goo…óndooje mon …óeen jamfondiro hakkunde mon, nde mofte [mon …óen] wonata …ďurde tonaade e dii mofte goo. ngandee Alla no jarribora on …óuum. ma o …ďanngina- na on √Īande darngal, …óuu ko luutondiratno…óon e mum."
  16,93,"Sinno Alla muuyuno, o wa…óatno on mofte goote. Kono, Himo majjina on Mo o muuyi, O feewna on mo O muuyi. ma on lannditoye e …óuu ko ngollatno…óon."
  16,94,"Wota on njogitor goo…óndooje mon jamfondiro hakkunde mon, sakko koyngal [mon] mortotoo (fergito) …ďaawo ngal tabitude, mee…óiron bone sabu ko paddi…óon ko e laawol Alla ngol. hino woodani on lepte maw…óe."
  16,95,"Wota on mba…ótitir ahadi Alla ndiin coggu pam…óungu. √Īganndee ko ko woni ka Alla ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īan¬īde on, si tawno ho…óon nganndi!"
  16,96,"Ko mar…óon kon re'ay (gasat), ko woni ka Alla ko ko keddotoo…óum. ma min mbarjor …ďeen mu√Ī√Īii…ďe njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndiin ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e ko …ďe ngollatnoo kon."
  16,97,"Kala gollu…óo mo∆ī∆īere, woni gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gooŇč…óin…óo, maa min wuurnu mo nguur- ndam laa…ďu…óam. Ma min mbaajor …ďe njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin, ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e ko …ďe ngollatnoo kon."
  16,98,"Si a janngay Alqur'aana, moolor Alla seytaane diiwaa…óo on."
  16,99,"KaŇčko on, mbawdi(cemmbe) alanaa mo e …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe, …ďe fawii e hoore Joomi ma…ď…ďe."
  16,100,"nganndee mbawdi makko ndiin, ko hoore …ďeen weldii…ďe e makko woni, e …ďeen sirkiroo…ďe sabu makko."
  16,101,"Si min lomtinii aaya lomto aaya goo - Ko Alla …ďuri anndude ko O jippinta - ∆Āe mbi'a: ""aan on ko a pekindii…óo"". Si ko woni, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe anndaa."
  16,102,"Maaku: ""Ko jippini ndee, ko [Jibriilu] Fittaanndu Laa…ďndu ndun, immorde ka Joomi maa, fii yo o tabintin …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe, e [fii yo nde won] peewal, e welo-welo wonan¬īde juul…ďe …ďeen""."
  16,103,"GooŇč…óii min mi…óen nganndi won¬īde he…ďe mbi'a: ""Ko ne…ó…óaŇčke woni mo anndinnde (Alqur'aana)"". ∆äemngal ngal …ďe oo√Īotoo e mun ngal ko ajami, ndee …óoo non ka …óemngal Aarabi …ďanngungal(.laa…ďtungal.)"
  16,104,"Pellet, …ďen …ďe ngooŇč…óinaani Aayeeje Alla …óeen, Alla feewnataa …ďe. Hino woodani …ďe lepte muus…óe."
  16,105,"Nganndee ko fejkindotoo fenaande, ko …ďeen …ďe ngoŇč…óinaani- aayee Alla …óen; ko kam…ďe ngooni fenoo…ďe …ďeen."
  16,106,"Kala jeddu…óo Alla …ďaawo gooŇč…óinal makko ngal - si wanaa on waawnaa…óo hara …ďernde makko nden ko dee∆īirnde gooŇč…óinal , kono, …ďeen ya√Ī√Īam…ďe …ďer…óe mun keeferaaku, hino fawii …ďe tikkere immorde Alla, hino woodani …ďe kadi lepte maw…óe."
  16,107,"Ngol [murtugol ma…ď…ďe], ko tawde …ďe cu…ďiima nguurndam aduna e dow laakara, e won¬īde Alla kan, O feewnataa yim…ďe yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  16,108,"Ko …ďeen ngoni …ďe Alla noti e …ďer…óe mum, e nan…óe mun e gite mum. Ko …ďeen ngooni welsindii…ďe …ďen."
  16,109,"Sikke alaaa won¬īde …ďeen …óoon ka laakara, ko kam…ďe ngoni sooy…ďe …ďeen."
  16,110,"refti pellet Joomi maa, wonannde …ďen ferunoo…ďe …ďaawo nde …ďe tampinaama, hooti …ďe tii…ónii …ďe mu√Ī√Īii, pellet Joomi maa, …ďaawo …óuum, Ko O jaafotoo…óo, jurmotoo…óo."
  16,111,"(JanŇčo) tuma √Īande kala woŇčkii arata, hara hiki wennja fii hoore-makki, woŇčkii kala yo…ďee ko ki golli kon, kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake."
  16,112,"Alla piyii misal ho…óo: ho…óo hoolinoongo, dee∆īungo; arsike maggo no ardirana ngo nokku kala e yaaj- jeende. ∆Āe njeddi dokke Alla …óe, Alla mee…óiniri …ďe kolgu heege e kulol, sabu ko …ďe ngollatnoo kon."
  16,113,"GooŇč…óii arii e ma…ď…ďe nulaa…óo jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe njeddi mo. Lepte …óeen nanngi …ďe, tawi ko …ďe too√Ī…ďe."
  16,114,"√Ďaamee e kon ko Alla arsike on dagii…ói laa…ďu…ói, njeetton dokke Alla …óeen, si wonii ko KaŇčko ndewoton."
  16,115,"nganndee ko o Harminani on, ko jiiba, e ∆īii∆īam (rufaa…óam), e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on du√Īaa…óo [e √Īaamugol …óuum] hara wonaa …ďew…óo wonaa jaggi- tu…óo,nganndee pellet, Allah ko jaatoo…óo jurmotoo…óo."
  16,116,"Wota on mbi'u ko …óem…óe mon sifotoo e penaale: ""∆äum …óoo no dagii, …óum …óoo no harmi"", fii no pekindoron e hoore Alla fenaande. Pellet, …ďen fekindotoo…ďe fenaande e hoore Alla, …ďe maletaake."
  16,117,"Ko dakamme pam…óu…óo, hino woodani …ďe lepte muus…óe."
  16,118,"E hoore Alyahuudaa…ďe …ďeen (kan), min karminno ko min fillani maa kon ko adii. min too√Īaano …ďe; ko woni, ko ko'e-ma…ď…ďe …ďe ngonnnoo e too√Īude."
  16,119,"Refti pellel, Joomi maa, wonan¬īde …ďeen gollu…ďe bone on majjere, refti …ďe tuubi …ďaawo …óuum …ďe mo∆ī∆īini, pellet Joomi maa, …ďaawo …óuum, ko jaafotoo…óo, jurmotoo…óo."
  16,120,"Pellet, Ibraahiima woniino …óowro koykinanii…óo Alla, oo√Īii…óo [e …óiya diinaaji], o wonaana jeyaa…óo e sirkoo…ďe …ďeen."
  16,121,"jettatnoo…óo dokke makko …óin. [Alla] su…ďike mo, O feewni mo e laawol poocciingol."
  16,122,"Min ngokki mo ka aduna mo∆ī∆īere. KaŇčko oon ka laakara, ko o jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďeen."
  16,123,"Refi min mbahayini e maa…óa, won¬īde: "" Jokku diina Ibraahiima ka naayaaki e diinaaji mehre o jeyanooka e sirkoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  16,124,"ngandee [mawningol fii] aseweere nden ko wa…óanaa, ko …ďeen luutondir…ďe e mayre. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko √Īaawoyoowo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Ďande Darngal, e …óuum ko …ďe luutondiratnoo fii mum."
  16,125,"Noddir e diina Joomi maa kan √Īee√Īal e waaju mo∆ī∆īu. Wennjiraa …ďe e noone …ďur…óo mo∆ī∆īude. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko KaŇčko …ďuri anndude on majju…óo e laawol makko ngol, ko KaŇčko kadi …ďuri anndi feew…ďe …ďeen."
  16,126,"Si on yagginay, haray yagginiree yeru no wa…óirano…óon non. Ko si on mu√Ī√Īike, pellet ko …óuum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īan¬īde mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďeen."
  16,127,"Mu√Ī√Īo! Mu√Īal maa ngal ko sabu Alla tan. wota a suno fii ma…ď…ďe. wota wonu …ďittor…óo e …óuum ko …ďe pewjata."
  16,128,"Pellet, Alla no won¬īdi e …ďeen hul…ďe [Mo] e …ďeen mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe."
